{"tid":1837322,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新加坡淪陷   確診首例武漢肺炎病例","createTime":"2020-01-23T14:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T15:21:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"530046860bdeb99dfe6fc534b616d329c26db41c","tid":1837322,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:46:50.000Z","msg":"據大陸央視新聞報導，新加坡衛生部23日晚確認，新加坡出現首例新型冠狀病毒病例，患者為一名66歲男子。另有一名53歲女子初步測試結果呈陽性，目前正在等待最終的檢測結果。 但報導並未進一步說明，兩人是否來自中國大陸或者是新加坡籍。<br />\n<br />\n此前大陸境外確診武漢肺炎病例的地區已有：泰國、日本、台灣、美國、韓國、香港及澳門。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120936/4305083?from=udn-catebreaknews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120936%2F4305083%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catebreaknews_ch2&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeKEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=ec546a9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120936/4305083?from=udn-catebreaknews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"a416455c639c0a12419b0035994f79c1e052e35f","tid":1837322,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:47:36.000Z","msg":"共享華人榮耀"},{"pid":"e44cbb46fb4ce4c2e5ee4e1fff82ba76afab324b","tid":1837322,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb79ad77b3f288bf4e704b0f0273a2f33cd3bf4d","tid":1837322,"uid":47259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但報導並未進一步說明，兩人是否來自中國大陸或者是新加坡籍。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好重要咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隻菌會睇人國籍先決定傳唔傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}